# Urzadzenia typu master na magistrali RS485
# |Adres|    Nazwa    | sl/zn |  us  |
# | 01h | termometr A |  1/12 | 1041 |
# | 02h | termometr B |  1/12 | 1041 |
# | 12h | termometr C |  1/12 | 1041 |
# | 03h |    ADC1     | 16/72 | 6250 |
# | 05h |     RTC     |  3/30 | 1736 |
# | 06h |      F1     |  2/16 | 1388 |
# | 07h |      F2     |  2/16 | 1388 |
# | 0Ch |     WDS     |  1/12 | 1041 |
# | 08h |     CPR     |  1/12 | 1041 |
# | 0Dh |   SHARP30   |  1/12 | 1041 |
# | 0Eh |    SR04     |  1/12 | 1041 |


